Your next question is from David Buck, Buckingham Research Group.
David G. Buck - The Buckingham Research Group Incorporated
It\'s on BOTOX and the outlook and the guidance. So if we look at the first quarter, you mentioned, David, there were some impact from Merz during the quarter. And that\'s now going away. Can you talk about why you decided to keep the $1.75 billion to $1.8 billion guidance? And what\'s the sense of the impact that you can give us in terms of what the numbers would have been in terms of growth if Merz was not in the market for the first quarter?
David E.I. Pyott
